调整为单一国产 C919 飞机。 金鹏航空方面表示，如此客机机队调整不仅是金鹏航空自身发展的需要，更是以实际行动响应国家号召，全力支持国产大飞机腾飞坚定决心的体现。 据介绍，依照飞机引进计划，2024 年四季度，金鹏航空将接收首架 C919 客机，成为全球首家运行 C919 的民营航司，并计划在 2027 年底完成引进共计 30 架 C919 客机。腾波音，改换 C919，总计 30 架！这家民营航司宣布：机队将清一色为国产大飞机 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-dfcfdd861e586891e56f3f0c0860dc7d_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654213432"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI4I/NxZqCvJo2EAMaCTEwNzY1ODU4NSCX6a6xBjAAOOYCQCByCTY1NDIxMzQzMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1714227287.832244", "card_id": "Q_651768796", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 66}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你知道哪些有故事的村庄名？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-be03e7b600f2c19b869e1e999ea5cedb_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/651768796"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4I/NxZqCvJo2EAMaCTEwNzExNTE1MiD63b2wBjAAOE1AIXIJNjUxNzY4Nzk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1714227287.832486", "card_id": "Q_654054222", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "作为一名小说作者，在读别人的作品时是以什么角度去读的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作为一名小说作者，在阅读别人的作品时，是应该以读者的角度去阅读，还是以作者的角度去阅读？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654054222"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I4I/NxZqCvJo2EAMaCTEwNzYyMzIzNSCppqex